
constraint/
	Contains Master xdc file (KCU105_master.xdc).
        Contains  xdc file (kcu105_ethernet.xdc) 
edn/
	processor_edn here.

toplevel/
	Contains the top level vhdl code of the SBC

hsys/
	We use this folder to construct our own core_library from highlevel to vhdl. It contains processor , Dram, Ethernet, serial and debug uarts
        Just do ./build.sh inside this folder (in the ajit-toolchain docker).

vivado_synth/
	Contains bitgen tcl file and run.sh script used to generate the bitfile and the working directory
	
ip/
	Contains the required ips.

configure_fpga/
	This folder contains the scripts and configuration files required to program the FPGA, perform reset sequencing, and initialize the hardware design through Vivado Hardware Manage
